<div class="row justify-content-md-center">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
            <h3 class="d-flex align-items-center">School Report</h3>
        </div>

        <p>
            <b>Results for school leadership team, school support staff, and teachers. </b>Best for users who have access to one school.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
            <h3 class="d-flex align-items-center">Region Report</h3>
        </div>

        <p>
            <b>
                Results for regional staff, school leadership team, school support staff, and teachers.
            </b> Best for users who have region access or access to multiple schools. Regional staff results only accessible to users with region access. Print report contains regional staff results only.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
            <h3 class="d-flex align-items-center">Match Counselor Report</h3>
        </div>

        <p>
